### Create a new post
# Expected:
# - Status: 200 OK
# - Response body contains:
#   - id: newly generated UUID
#   - authorId: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
#   - hobbyId: 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
#   - content: "This is my first post in this hobby"
#   - likeCount: 0
#   - commentCount: 0
#   - createdAt: current timestamp
POST http://localhost:8082/posts
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

{
  "hobbyId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "content": "This is my first post in this hobby"
}


### Create another post
# Expected:
# - Status: 200 OK
# - New post created with a different id
# - Same authorId and hobbyId as above
# - createdAt is later than the first post
POST http://localhost:8082/posts
Content-Type: application/json
X-User-Id: 11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111

{
  "hobbyId": "22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222",
  "content": "Second post under the same hobby"
}


### Get posts by hobby
# Expected:
# - Status: 200 OK
# - Response is a JSON array
# - Array contains both posts created above
# - Posts are ordered by createdAt DESC (newest first)
# - All posts have hobbyId = 22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222
GET http://localhost:8082/posts/hobby/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222?limit=10


### Get posts by author
# Expected:
# - Status: 200 OK
# - Response is a JSON array
# - Array contains all posts created by author:
#   11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111
# - Posts are ordered by createdAt DESC
GET http://localhost:8082/posts/user/11111111-1111-1111-1111-111111111111?limit=10


### Get post by ID
# Expected:
# - Status: 200 OK if post exists
# - Response body matches the post with the given id
# - If the ID does not exist:
#   - Status: 404 Not Found
GET http://localhost:8082/posts/<POST_ID>


### Get posts by hobby with cursor
# Expected:
# - Status: 200 OK
# - Response is a JSON array with at most 1 post (limit=1)
# - Returned post has createdAt < <CURSOR_INSTANT>
# - Used to simulate infinite scrolling
GET http://localhost:8082/posts/hobby/22222222-2222-2222-2222-222222222222?limit=1&cursor=<CURSOR_INSTANT>


